        public void checkOTA(java.lang.String otaType)
        Set the firmware upgrade type 0 upgrade firmware 1.Upgrade the default dynamic watch face 2.Upgrade small fonts 3. Upgrade large fonts 4. Upgrade UI image resources 5. Upgrade 2, 3, 4 at the same time 6.push sport mode 7.Incremental upgrade ui 8.Upgrade multiple dial compression 255.discard current upgrade 10+n Upgrade dynamic dial 20+n Upgrade custom watch faces
        参数:
        otaType - FissionConstant OTA_TYPE_

        duration - current exercise duration(in seconds)

      • replyControlGpsSportResult

        public void replyControlGpsSportResult(int sportType,
                                       int sportStatus,
                                       int result,
                                       int duration)
        Respond to commands when the device controls the app gps movement
        参数:
        sportType - FissionEnum SPORT_
        sportStatus - FissionConstant GPS_SPORT_ 1 == start; 2 == pause; 3 == continue; 4 == recover(After bluetooth is disconnected and reconnected)
        result - FissionConstant GPS_SPORT_RESULT_ 10 == normal execution; 11 == Already implemented, consistent with the current state; 12 == Low battery, unable to execute; 13 == command status error; 14 == You are exercising regularly, please stop exercising first; 15 == During a call, unable to execute
        duration - current exercise duration(in seconds)
